3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20a%20key%20theme%20was%20%26quot%3BIndustries%20in%20the%20Intelligent%20Age.%26quot%3B%20Attendees%20discussed%20topics%20ranging%20from%20AI's%20impact%20on%20manufacturing%20to%20whether%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20will%20be%20a%20force%20for%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20more%20heads%20of%20state%2C%20AI%20researchers%2C%20and%20regulators%20flocked%20to%20Paris%20for%20the%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20Action%20Summit.%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20%E2%80%94%20who%20co-hosted%20the%20conference%20with%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%94%20promised%20that%20France%20would%20cut%20back%20the%20red%20tape%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Vice%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvance-swipes-at-eu-in-ai-summit-speech-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJD%20Vance%20told%20the%20summit's%20attendees%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Bmassive%26quot%3B%20regulations%20could%20constrict%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20technology.%20AI%20leaders%2C%20like%20DeepMind%20CEO%20Demis%20Hassabis%2C%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20international%20cooperation%20on%20regulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20this%20month%2C%20thousands%20of%20startup%20founders%2C%20investors%2C%20and%20technologists%20are%20expected%20to%20descend%20upon%20Las%20Vegas%20for%20HumanX%20%E2%80%94%20an%20event%20that%20bills%20itself%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20important%20AI%20conference%20of%20the%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecutives%20from%20companies%20like%20OpenAI%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Anthropic%2C%20investors%20from%20Sequoia%20Capital%20and%20Khosla%20Ventures%2C%20and%20politicians%20like%20former%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20will%20gather%20from%20March%209-13%20at%20the%20Fontainebleau%20to%20talk%20about%20topics%20ranging%20from%20compliance%20in%20the%20AI%20age%20to%20using%20the%20technology%20to%20unlock%20new%20forms%20of%20creativity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20will%20feature%20about%20330%20speakers%20and%20organizers%20expect%20over%203%2C000%20attendees.%20Tickets%20cost%20about%20%243%2C200%20for%20general%20admission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221278%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22HumanX%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c4e05db8b41a9673f96e17%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20dominated%20funding%20in%202024.%3Cp%3EHumanX%2FCrunchbase%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHumanX%20was%20co-founded%20by%20event%20veteran%20Jonathan%20Weiner%20%E2%80%94%20who%20has%20launched%20large-scale%20conferences%20like%20HLTH%2C%20Shoptalk%2C%20and%20Money20%2F20%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Stefan%20Weitz%2C%20an%20alum%20of%20Microsoft%20and%20an%20entrepreneur%20and%20investor.%20The%20pair%20raised%20%246.2%20million%20in%20funding%20for%20the%20event%20in%20a%20round%20led%20by%20New%20York-based%20Primary%20Ventures%2C%20along%20with%20Foundation%20Capital%20and%20FPV%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeitz%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20fundraising%20wasn't%20hard.%20The%20firms%20%E2%80%94%20which%20back%20dozens%20of%20AI%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20saw%20the%20conference%20as%20another%20vehicle%20to%20build%20momentum%20for%20their%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20could%20even%20look%20at%20it%20as%20almost%20promoting%20their%20own%20book%2C%20right%3F%20They%20need%20these%20AI%20companies%20to%20be%20successful%2C%20which%20they%20need%20to%20have%20enterprises%20purchasing%20those%20solutions%2C%20and%20not%20churning%20after%20a%20year%20when%20the%20SaaS%20contract%20is%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Weitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20it's%20imperative%20to%20the%20whole%20ecosystem%20that%20we%20get%20out%20of%20the%20pilot%20purgatory%20that%20we've%20been%20sitting%20in%20for%20a%20while%20and%20actually%20start%20moving%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPilot%20purgatory%2C%20as%20defined%20by%20McKinsey%2C%20is%20a%20state%20in%20which%20companies%20have%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20activity%20underway%2C%20but%20are%20not%20yet%20seeing%20meaningful%20bottom-line%20benefits%20from%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221658%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AI%20funding%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c4e0cab1834fe31165e8f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22802%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E2024%20was%20a%20banner%20year%20for%20AI%20funding%20across%20the%20world.%3Cp%3EHumanX%2FCrunchbase%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDizzying%20levels%20of%20funding%20have%20fueled%20the%20AI%20industry.%20In%202024%2C%20over%20%24100%20billion%20went%20to%20AI%20startups%2C%20accounting%20for%20a%20third%20of%20all%20global%20startup%20funding%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20that%20HumanX%20released%20in%20partnership%20with%20Crunchbase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20established%20players%20like%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20collected%20almost%20a%20third%20of%20last%20year's%20AI%20funding%20and%20companies%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20landed%20the%20majority%20(about%2060%25)%2C%20more%20money%20also%20flowed%20to%20sectors%20deeper%20in%20the%20AI%20ecosystem%20%E2%80%94%20from%20companies%20building%20the%20hardware%20and%20software%20that%20supports%20large%20language%20models%20to%20applications%20built%20on%20top%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20also%20giving%20Wall%20Street%20a%20wake-up%20call%20as%20it%20braces%20itself%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-investment-bankers-for-generative-ai-acquisitions-capital-raising-advice%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewave%20of%20AI-related%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Of%20the%20153%20private%20AI%20companies%20appearing%20at%20HumanX%2C%2029%25%20are%20targeted%20for%20acquisitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHumanX's%20panels%20will%20largely%20focus%20on%20propelling%20growth%20across%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20AI%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Weitz%20describes%20it%2C%20HumanX%20will%20highlight%20%26quot%3Bthe%20great%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3Bnew%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20companies%20are%20doing%20with%20that%20new%20stuff.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20also%20be%20discussions%20on%20how%20to%20regulate%20all%20this%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20that%2C%20Harris%2C%20the%20former%20vice%20president%20who%20served%20as%20the%20AI%20czar%20during%20the%20Biden%20Administration%2C%20will%20make%20an%20appearance%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eshare%20her%20vision%20for%20responsibly%20developing%20the%20technology.%20Harris%2C%20who%20previously%20described%20the%20technology%20as%20%26quot%3Bkind%20of%20a%20fancy%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20largely%20been%20seen%20as%20a%20moderate%2C%20dismissing%20the%20idea%20of%20choosing%20between%20AI%20regulation%20and%20innovation%20as%20a%20false%20binary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20catalyzed%20a%20wave%20of%20global%20change%2C%20and%20Weitz%20said%20his%20team%20has%20already%20been%20approached%20about%20setting%20up%20HumanX%20events%20in%20other%20regions%2C%20including%20Europe%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%20For%20now%2C%20though%2C%20he's%20just%20hoping%20the%20inaugural%20conference%20goes%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20one%20of%20those%20things%20where%20we're%20one%20foot%20in%20front%20of%20the%20other.%20Let's%20deliver%20the%20best%20thing%20we%20can%2C%20and%20then%20we'll%20move%20on%20from%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20things%20take%20no%20less%20than%20nine%20months%20and%20preferably%20a%20year%20to%20pull%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhumanx-ai-conference-las-vegas-what-to-expect-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness