down%20website%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20movement%20against%20Musk%20started%20on%20Bluesky%20between%20friends%20and%20activists%20and%20snowballed%20when%20he%20created%20the%20webpage%20to%20help%20centralize%20the%20effort.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Los%20Angeles-based%20director%20and%20writer%20said%20that%20while%20he%20was%20initially%20not%20expecting%20a%20significant%20response%2C%20thousands%20of%20people%20now%20visit%20the%20website%20every%20hour%2C%20and%20they%20have%20hundreds%20of%20events%20planned%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnline%20disinformation%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20far-right%20has%20been%20a%20peak%20area%20of%20interest%20for%20me%20for%20a%20long%20time%20in%20my%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Winter%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20concerned%20about%20Elon%20Musk%20back%20since%20he%20was%20at%20PayPal%2C%20and%20then%20with%20the%20purchase%20and%20dismantling%20of%20Twitter%2C%20and%20now%20it%20has%20reared%20its%20head%20in%20a%20way%20that%20I%20think%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20has%20woken%20up%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scene%20at%20this%20California%20showroom%20was%20just%20one%20of%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-takedown-protests-photos-2025-2%23multiple-protests-happened-in-san-francisco-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotests%20scheduled%20at%20Tesla%20retail%20locations%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20country%2C%20all%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20display%20of%20discontent%20against%20Musk%20over%20his%20involvement%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDOGE's%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20efforts%20to%20decrease%20the%20size%20of%20the%20federal%20workforce.%20Many%20are%20also%20critical%20of%20a%20gesture%20Musk%20made%20during%20Trump's%20inauguration%20festivities