0past%20five%20quarters%2C%20falling%20by%2011.6%25%20in%202024%20compared%20to%20the%20year%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrian%20Maas%2C%20president%20of%20the%20California%20New%20Car%20Dealers%20Association%2C%20said%20that%20though%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-stock-sales-slide-elon-musk-doge-trump-electric-vehicles-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla's%20decline%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20state's%20green%20energy%20transition%20as%20the%20manufacturer%20with%20the%20largest%20market%20share%2C%20other%20zero-emission%20car%20makers%20are%20ready%20to%20step%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20happened%20to%20Tesla%2C%20among%20many%2C%20many%20other%20factors%2C%20is%20there's%20robust%20competition%20now%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyd-xpeng-china-ev-crushing-tesla-going-global-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ezero-emission%20vehicle%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20just%20didn't%20exist%2010%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20Maas%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20number%20of%20manufacturers%20out%20there%20have%20really%20spent%20incredible%20time%2C%20money%2C%20and%20effort%20to%20carve%20out%20and%20build%20a%20niche%20in%20the%20EV%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20Atlantic%2C%20Tesla%20also%20suffered%20a%20decline%20in%20sales.%20According%20to%20data%20from%20the%20European%20Automobile%20Manufacturers'%20Association%2C%20Tesla%20sold%209%2C945%20vehicles%20in%20Europe%20in%20January%2C%20down%2045%25%20from%20last%20year's%2018%2C161%20in%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20drugstore%20chain%20Dirk%20Rossmann%20GmbH%20and%20energy%20company%20LichtBlick%20also%20announced%20a%20few%20months%20apart%20that%20they%20would%20no%20longer%20purchase%20Tesla%20vehicles%20for%20their%20company%20fleets%2C%20citing%20Musk's%20support%20for%20Trump%20and%20right-wing%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharles%20Cho%2C%20a%20California%20resident%20who%20bought%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-model-y%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20Model%20Y%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%20for%20around%20%2460%2C000%2C%20including%20tax%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20despite%20having%20had%20to%20fix%20the%20vehicle%2015%20times%20within%20two%20years%20because%20it%20frequently%20experienced%20failures%2C%20Musk's%20behavior%20made%20him%20determined%20to%20get%20his%20money%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecently%2C%20with%20all%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20antics%20and%20doing%20the%20Nazi%20salute%2C%20it%20is%20just%20not%20a%20good%20look%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cho%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20even%20want%20to%20drive%20this%20Tesla%20anymore%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20seen%20with%20it%20in%20public.%20So%20I%20got%20a%20lawyer%20who%20helped%20me%20negotiate%20a%20full%20buyback.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECho%20said%20he%20originally%20bought%20the%20car%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20emissions%20and%20because%20its%20technology%20seemed%20revolutionary.%20After%20giving%20up%20the%20Tesla%20in%20February%2C%20he%20put%20in%20an%20order%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frivian-r2-suv-release-price-range-specs-photos-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERivian%20R2%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20will%20be%20released%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Protestors%20parade%20a%20cybertruck%20model%20made%20of%20cardboard%20box%20%20down%20the%20block%20in%20Berkeley%2C%20California%2C%20during%20a%20demonstration%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Tesla%20showroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c415f1b8b41a9673f96b31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProtesters%20parade%20a%20cybertruck%20model%20made%20of%20cardboard%20box%20down%20the%20block%20in%20Berkeley%2C%20California%2C%20during%20a%20demonstration%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Tesla%20showroom.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Li%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20in%20management%20and%20policy%20have%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20public%20pressure%20is%20unlikely%20to%20change%20Musk's%20behavior.%20Still%2C%20his%20days%20as%20a%20close%20aide%20to%20Trump%20may%20be%20numbered%20if%20anger%20against%20him%20spills%20over%20to%20Trump's%20poll%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20what%20I%20know%20of%20Musk%2C%20he%20is%20not%20one%20to%20give%20in%20to%20public%20pressure%20and%20may%20even%20see%20this%20as%20a%20fun%20challenge%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Larry%20Gerston%2C%20professor%20emeritus%20of%20public%20policy%20at%20San%20Jose%20State%20University.%20However%2C%20he%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20his%20policies%20at%20DOGE%20generate%20a%20sufficient%20backlash%2C%20and%20that%20backlash%20piggybacks%20onto%20resentment%20for%20Trump%2C%20then%20Trump%20will%20cut%20him%20loose%2C%20and%20his%20megaphone%20may%20be%20diminished.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20anybody's%20about%20to%20send%20or%20chase%20Musk%20away%20because%20he%20is%20Tesla%2C%20and%20there%20is%20little%20separating%20the%20two%2C%26quot%3B%20Gerston%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Kellie%20McElhaney%2C%20an%20expert%20in%20organization%20management%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20distinguished%20teaching%20fellow%20at%20UC%20Berkeley's%20Haas%20School%20of%20Business%20said%20that%20as%20the%20wealthiest%20man%20in%20the%20world%2C%20Musk%20is%20diversified%20enough%20in%20assets%20that%20a%20boycott%20against%20Tesla%20is%20insufficient%20to%20prevent%20him%20from%20doing%20as%20he%20pleases%2C%20but%20such%20a%20movement%20allows%20people%20to%20feel%20empowered%20during%20a%20time%20when%20it's%20easy%20to%20feel%20completely%20powerless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20individual%20consumer%20truck%20sales%20or%20car%20sales%20can%20be%20down%2C%20but%20if%20the%20current%20government%20can%20promise%20to%20buy%20a%20fleet%2C%20there%20will%20probably%20be%20no%20negative%20impact%20on%20Tesla%2C%26quot%3B%20McElhaney%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20maybe%20we%20focus%20too%20much%20on%20the%20financial%20impact%20on%20the%20brand%20when%20the%20right%20focus%20is%20the%20human%20impact%20of%20feeling%20like%20we%20have%20powers%2C%20which%20is%20a%20better%20metric.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-showroom-protests-boycott-elon-musk-doge-cybertruck-ev-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740996301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c3e409b8b41a9673f96b0a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-showroom-protests-boycott-elon-musk-doge-cybertruck-ev-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20protests%20are%20growing%20nationwide%20as%20anger%20grows%20over%20Elon%20Musk's%20ties%20to%20Trump%20and%20DOGE.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Li)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-showroom-protests-boycott-elon-musk-doge-cybertruck-ev-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20hedge%20funds%20became%20an%20industry%20of%20haves%20and%20have-nots%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20what%20it%20means%20for%20the%20%244.5%20trillion%20sector%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22big%20four%20hedge%20fund%20thumb%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67be3a98b8b41a9673f8f730%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Darko%2FGetty%2C%20skodonnell%2FGetty%2C%20angel_nt%2FGetty%2C%20Klaus%20Vedfelt%2FGetty%2C%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20it%20was%20common%20knowledge%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aurum.com%2Finsight%2Fthought-piece%2Felephant-in-the-room-size-and-hedge-fund-performance%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmaller%20hedge%20funds%20outperformed%20larger%20peers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20focused%20on%20finding%20up-and-coming%20managers%20before%20they%20made%20it%20big%20and%20raised%20billions.%20Big-name%20institutions%20like%20Blackstone%20and%20the%20Teacher%20Retirement%20System%20of%20Texas%20seeded%20new%20funds%20and%20sought%20out%20emerging%20managers.%20While%20there%20was%20safety%20and%2C%20typically%2C%20capacity%20in%20the%20biggest%20funds%2C%20there%20was%20alpha%20in%20unknown%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20all%20changed%20with%20the%20yearslong%20industry%20takeover%20by%20the%20biggest%20multistrategy%20firms.%20The%20big%20four%20%E2%80%94%20Millennium%2C%20Citadel%2C%20Point72%2C%20and%20Balyasny%20%E2%80%94%20have%20in%20recent%20years%20outperformed%20peers%20despite%20their%20ballooning%20sizes%2C%20dominated%20the%20fundraising%20environment%20even%20though%20they're%20mostly%20closed%20to%20new%20money%2C%20and%20turned%20the%20talent%20market%20on%20its%20head%20with%20eye-popping%20offers%20for%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FZFc3O%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Average%20multistrategy%20hedge%20fund%202024%20returns%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22488%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20scale%20benefits%20both%20the%20manager%20and%20the%20LP%2C%20and%20the%20result%20is%20four%20managers%20with%20overwhelming%20clout.%20Business%20Insider%20talked%20to%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20fund%20founders%2C%20allocators%2C%20and%20industry%20experts%2C%20such%20as%20top%20prime%20brokers%20and%20recruiters%2C%20to%20understand%20how%20smaller%20platforms%20plan%20to%20survive%20the%20unprecedented%20concentration%20of%20capital%20and%20talent%20and%20where%20allocators%20are%20turning%20in%20this%20new%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs'%20prime%20brokerage%20desk%2C%20using%20regulatory%20filings%2C%20estimated%20in%20July%20that%2053%20multistrategy%20firms%20employed%20a%20total%20of%2018%2C600%20people.%20More%20than%2071%25%20of%20them%20worked%20for%20one%20of%20the%20big%20four%2C%20leaving%20the%2049%20other%20funds%20with%20a%20combined%20head%20count%20smaller%20than%20Millennium's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FyIzOb%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Hedge%20fund%20headcount%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22451%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EFundraising%20%E2%80%94%20which%20came%20easy%20for%20big%20and%20small%20platforms%20alike%20when%20interest%20rates%20were%20lower%20three%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20is%20now%20a%20slog%20for%20many%20smaller%20multistrategy%20funds%2C%20several%20executives%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20shift%20has%20cramped%20some%20firms'%20expansion%20plans%20that%20commenced%20during%20the%20boom%20times%20following%20the%20pandemic%20and%20put%20pressure%20on%20a%20business%20model%20that%20thrives%20with%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Point72%20and%20Citadel%20have%20returned%20capital%20to%20investors%2C%20and%20Millennium%20can%20command%20a%20five-year%20lockup%20period%20for%20new%20money%2C%20a%20term%20length%20previously%20unheard%20of%20in%20the%20hedge%20fund%20world.%20One%20allocator%20told%20BI%20that%20Point72%2C%20the%20%2439%20billion%20firm%20run%20by%20the%20billionaire%20New%20York%20Mets%20owner%20Steve%20Cohen%2C%20had%20a%20%249%20billion%20waitlist%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20more%20capital%20than%20firms%20like%20Eisler%20and%20Walleye%20manage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20different%20allocator%20compared%20the%20concentration%20of%20capital%20in%20the%20four%20largest%20firms%20to%20passive%20investing%2C%20in%20which%20all%20the%20assets%20flow%20to%20Vanguard%2C%20BlackRock%2C%20or%20State%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20people%20who%20can't%20get%20into%20the%20top%20guys%2C%20they're%20saying%20they'll%20just%20invest%20in%20some%20other%20structure%20or%20asset%20class%20instead%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20person%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20private%20credit%20as%20a%20landing%20spot%20for%20some%20of%20this%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a498d5b-1ace-4988-9530-4712174c97aa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDavid%20vs.%204%20Goliaths%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20four%20platforms%20have%20grown%20to%20a%20point%20where%20smaller%20rivals%20aren't%20battling%20another%20hedge%20fund%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20fighting%20with%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20becoming%20more%20and%20more%20like%20investment%20banks%20to%20an%20extent%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20platform%20founder%20with%20less%20than%20%2410%20billion%20in%20total%20assets.%20Others%20in%20the%20industry%20likened%20Citadel%20in%20particular%20to%20pre-IPO%20Goldman%20Sachs%20%E2%80%94%20a%20comparison%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fken-griffin-modeled-citadel-after-old-school-goldman-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKen%20Griffin%20would%20most%20likely%20welcome%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20given%20his%20laudatory%20comments%20about%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20hypothetical%20%245%20billion%20multistrategy%20manager%20has%20a%20much%20different%20existence%20than%20even%20the%20%2421%20billion%20firm%20Balyasny.%20One%20smaller%20platform%20executive%20hoping%20to%20grow%20said%20that%2C%20even%20as%20Citadel%20and%20Point72%20returned%20capital%20to%20LPs%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20a%20bitch%20last%20year%20raising%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FzRsEL%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Hedge%20fund%20assets%20under%20management%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22475%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EA%20February%20report%20from%20JPMorgan's%20capital%20advisory%20team%20said%20hedge%20funds%20with%20assets%20between%20%24500%20million%20and%20%245%20billion%20had%20net%20outflows%20of%20%2421.5%20billion%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20while%20firms%20with%20assets%20greater%20than%20%245%20billion%20hauled%20in%20%2412.2%20billion%20in%20net%20new%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs'%20July%20report%20noted%20that%20allocators%20were%20starting%20to%20balk%20at%20the%20high%20costs%20required%20to%20run%20multistrategy%20firms.%20The%20trickle-down%20effect%20is%20that%20firms%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexoduspoint-multistrategy-hedge-funds-lower-fees-adopt-cash-hurdle-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EExodusPoint%20have%20accepted%20a%20cash%20hurdle%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20where%20performance%20fees%20accrue%20only%20when%20returns%20surpass%20that%20of%20a%20Treasury%20bond%20%E2%80%94%20to%20appease%20antsy%20LPs.%20Despite%20the%20buzz%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-bobby-jain-has-hired-jain-capital-hedge-fund-launch-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20launch%20of%20Jain%20Global%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20firm%20raised%20billions%20less%20than%20it%20was%20expected%20to%20pull%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20smaller-platform%20executives%20said%20LPs%20were%20also%20worried%20about%20a%20platform%20unwind%20and%20what%20a%20significant%20market%20event%20could%20do%20to%20these%20firms%2C%20given%20that%20they%20operate%20with%20so%20much%20leverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20capital%20in%20multistrategy%20funds%20than%20ever%20before%2C%20some%20market%20watchers%20have%20been%20sounding%20the%20alarm%20about%20the%20knock-on%20effects%20of%20this%20investing%20style.%20These%20funds%20use%20borrowed%20money%20to%20juice%20their%20bets%2C%20meaning%20any%20significant%20movement%20against%20their%20position%20can%20cause%20losses%20to%20accumulate%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20risk-management%20systems%20of%20these%20platforms%20will%20often%20force%20their%20investors%20to%20shed%20positions%20quickly%20in%20the%20face%20of%20mounting%20losses%2C%20which%20can%20exacerbate%20a%20stock's%20decline.%20It's%20a%20market%20risk%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fviking-global-pm-worried-about-multi-strat-meltdown-cfrhf-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EViking%20Global's%20chief%20investment%20officer%2C%20Justin%20Walsh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20he%20monitors%20closely%20and%20that%20the%20governor%20of%20the%20Bank%20of%20England%2C%20Andrew%20Bailey%2C%20raised%20concerns%20about%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20that%20scale%20has%20become%20necessary%20for%20those%20competing%20directly%20with%20the%20four%20biggest%20firms%2C%20any%20slowdown%20in%20growth%20can%20be%20fatal%2C%20and%20suddenly%20tepid%20allocators%20could%20cause%20a%20domino%20effect%2C%20a%20former%20hedge%20fund%20allocator%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20capital%2C%20you%20can't%20get%20a%20diversity%20of%20return%20streams%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BWithout%20a%20diversity%20of%20return%20streams%2C%20the%20model%20doesn't%20really%20make%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c076dd6d-a21b-44e4-a8b7-99e29deed7c1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Do%20you%20have%20a%20right%20to%20exist%3F'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20that%20can't%20beat%20the%20biggest%20players%20at%20their%20own%20game%20need%20to%20offer%20something%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20going%20to%20compete%20with%20Citadel%20and%20Millennium%20in%20their%20own%20backyard%2C%20you're%20already%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20who's%20building%20out%20their%20multistrategy%20offering%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20have%20a%20right%20to%20exist%20%E2%80%94%20or%20are%20you%20on%20borrowed%20time%20because%20you%20raised%20money%20when%20all%20multistrats%20could%20raise%20money%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Barrett%2C%20the%20head%20of%20manager%20research%20at%20Kepler%20Partners%2C%20who%20works%20with%20allocators%20searching%20for%20funds%2C%20said%20smaller%20platforms%20must%20offer%20a%20%26quot%3Bderivative%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20main%20models%20the%20big%20four%20have%20perfected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Dymon%20Asia%2C%20a%20%243%20billion%20multistrategy%20fund%20with%20offices%20in%20Asia%20and%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fasia-multi-strat-hedge-funds-booming-tapping-middle-east-talent-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20differentiator%20is%20geography%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225271%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SummitTX%20CIO%20Caroline%20Cooley%20pictured%20in%20her%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670646c3a703186492807478%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225271%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaroline%20Cooley%2C%20the%20CIO%20of%20Fort%20Worth%2C%20Texas-based%20SummitTX.%3Cp%3ESummitTX%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20SummitTX%2C%20Crestline%20Investors'%20recently%20rebranded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-crestline-summit-expansion-plans-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultistrategy%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhat%