fth-floor%20walk-up%20trying%20to%20teach%20him%20where%20%E2%80%94%20and%20where%20not%20%E2%80%94%20to%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20never%20expected%20that%20%E2%80%94%20after%20being%20in%20this%20international%20bubble%20for%20so%20many%20years%20%E2%80%94%20getting%20a%20puppy%2C%20specifically%20a%20dachshund%2C%20would%20change%20this%20dynamic.%20Turns%20out%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ficonic-dachshund-faces-ban-germany-health-problems-reports-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGermans%20love%20dachshunds%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20soon%20as%20Toby%20hit%20the%20streets%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20smiles%20went%20from%2030%25%20to%2080%25.%20From%20our%20grumpy%20downstairs%20neighbor%20to%20the%20grandma%20and%20her%20grandchild%20across%20the%20street%2C%20we%20were%20met%20with%20curiosity%20and%20excitement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoving%20to%20Berlin%20hasn't%20been%20easy.%20I've%20faced%20challenges%2C%20loneliness%2C%20and%20moments%20of%20doubt.%20However%2C%20I'm%20happier%20living%20here%20than%20I%20ever%20was%20living%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlus%2C%20I've%20built%20a%20life%20full%20of%20incredible%20memories%20and%20am%20blessed%20to%20experience%20a%20culture%20so%20different%20from%20my%20own.%20I%20wouldn't%20trade%20it%20for%20the%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-us-to-berlin-felt-accepted-7-years-later-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740995642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0faa5b1834fe31165be94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-us-to-berlin-felt-accepted-7-years-later-2025-2%22%2C%22summary