our%20or%20five%20surfaces%20that%20are%20being%20used%20here.%20See%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20which%20pitch%20is%20going%20to%20be%20played%20in%20the%20semifinals.%20But%20whatever%20happens%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20adapt%20and%20see%20what%20is%20happening%20and%20what%20is%20not.%20And%20we%20will%20play%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20cited%20India's%20last%20Group%20A%20match%20against%20New%20Zealand%20on%20Sunday%20to%20emphasize%20his%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20that%20when%20the%20(New%20Zealand)%20bowlers%20were%20bowling%2C%20it%20was%20swinging%20a%20little%20bit.%20We%20did%20not%20see%20it%20in%20the%20first%20two%20games%20when%20our%20bowlers%20were%20bowling.%20In%20the%20last%20game%2C%20we%20did%20not%20get%20to%20see%20that%20much%20spin%2C%20today%20there%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20there%20are%20different%20things%20happening%20on%20every%20surface.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20not%20like%20we%20know%20what%20is%20going%20to%20happen%20on%20this%20pitch%20and%20what%20is%20not%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbaikar%20said%20a%20pitch%20with%20some%20assistance%20for%20the%20bowlers%20would%20make%20the%20contest%20all%20the%20more%20exciting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20something%20in%20it%20for%20the%20bowlers%20as%20well%2C%20that%20makes%20it%20very%2C%20very%20interesting.%20I%20am%20one%20for%20it.%20When%20you%20have%20surfaces%20which%20are%20challenging%2C%20whether%20it's%20with%20spin%20or%20with%20the%20seam%2C%20you%20want%20to%20have%20that.%20You%20want%20a%20good%20contest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20also%20vindicated%20the%20selection%20of%20five%20spinners%20in%20the%20India%20squad%20for%20the%20marquee%20event%20saying%20they%20had%20some%20awareness%20about%20the%20pitches%20in%20Dubai%20because%20they%20were%20monitoring%20the%20ILT20%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20the%20surface%20here%2C%20hearing%20about%20what%20has%20happened%20in%20Dubai%20in%20the%20past%20two%20months%2C%20we%20somehow%20kind%20of%20knew%20that%20surfaces%20are%20going%20to%20be%20slow.%20We%20were%20watching%20ILT20%20which%20was%20played%20here%20and%20we%20thought%20the%20slower%20bowlers%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20helpful%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20need%20an%20extra%20batter%20then%20anyway%20Rishabh%20(Pant)%20is%20there.%20So%2C%20we%20thought%20with%20an%20extra%20option%20of%20the%20spin%2C%20there%20is%20always%20a%20chance%20that%20we%20can%20play%20those%20guys%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2037-year-old%20said%20reaching%20Dubai%20well%20in%20advance%20helped%20the%20team%20to%20%E2%80%9Cadapt%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20important%20for%20us%20to%20adapt%20quickly%20to%20these%20conditions.%20Luckily%2C%20we%20came%20here%20five%20or%20six%20days%20before%2C%20we%20had%20good%20training%20sessions%20and%20the%20pitches%20at%20the%20(ICC)%20Academy%20were%20very%20much%20similar%20to%20what%20we%20are%20going%20to%20get%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20the%20adaptation%20is%20the%20key%20when%20you%20play%20on%20any%20surface%20and%20we%20adapted%20pretty%20well%20in%20all%20three%20games%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740995400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ft2hfuse8_ds_625x300_03_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fthis-is-not-our-home-rohit-sharma-breaks-silence-on-unfair-advantage-controversy-7836370%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20struck%20down%20the%20notion%20of%20India%20having%20an%20unfair%20advantage%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20due%20to%20playing%20all%20their%20matches%20in%20Dubai%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20not%20their%20%26quot%3Bhome%20venue%26quo