0over%2045%2C000%20stores%20globally%20%E2%80%94%20franchisees%20and%20self-owned%20%E2%80%94%20as%20of%20September%20last%20year.%20It%20has%20outpaced%20Starbucks%20and%20McDonald's%20retail%20footprints%2C%20which%20have%20around%2040%2C000%20and%2041%2C000%20outlets%20worldwide%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20jumped%20more%20than%2030%25%20to%20%24262%20when%20markets%20opened%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20first%20day%20of%20trading%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%20When%20markets%20closed%20on%20Monday%2C%20it%20was%20trading%20at%20%24294%2C%2045%25%20higher%20than%20its%20IPO%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain's%20founder%2C%20Zhang%20Hongchao%2C%20and%20his%20younger%20brother%2C%20Zhang%20Hongfu%2C%20have%20a%20combined%20net%20worth%20of%20%248.1%20billion%20after%20the%20share%20sale%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported%20on%20Sunday%2C%20citing%20its%20billionaires%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22588e9647-16cd-40de-acf7-4a95463d5e8a%5C%22%3E%241%20ice%20cream%2C%20%242%20drinks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMixue's%20main%20draw%20is%20its%20cheap%20products%2C%20customers%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20has%20around%2020%20outlets%20in%20Singapore%2C%20all%20operating%20as%20to-go%20counters.%20When%20BI%20visited%20an%20outlet%20near%20Singapore's%20Central%20Business%20District%20at%20around%20noon%20on%20Monday%2C%20there%20were%20around%20five%20people%20in%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20storefront's%20most%20prominent%20visual%20was%20the%20brand's%20%26quot%3BSnow%20King%26quot%3B%20mascot%20%E2%80%94%20a%20snowman%20wearing%20a%20crown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cheapest%20item%20at%20the%20store%20BI%20visited%20was%20the%20%241.10%20Signature%20King%20Cone%20ice%20cream%2C%20while%20the%20most%20expensive%20item%20was%20the%20Cheese%20Strawberry%20drink%2C%20priced%20at%20%243.%20Most%20of%20the%20store's%20drinks%20were%20sold%20in%20the%20%242%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223594%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mixue's%20products%20in%20Singapore%20were%20largely%20priced%20under%20SG%20%244.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c55de369253ccddf980c0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222630%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20most%20expensive%20menu%20item%20at%20the%20Mixue%20outlet%20BI%20visited%20was%20the%20Cheese%20Strawberry%20drink%2C%20which%20was%20%243.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEden%20Loke%2C%2023%2C%20a%20communications%20executive%2C%20said%20she%20first%20heard%20of%20Mixue%20when%20someone%20wearing%20the%20brand's%20inflatable%20%26quot%3BSnow%20King%26quot%3B%20mascot%20was%20filmed%20prancing%20around%20at%20a%20shopping%20complex%20in%20Singapore.%20The%20mascot's%20shenanigans%20at%20the%20mall%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20dance-off%20with%20another%20brand's%20mascot%20%E2%80%94%20went%20viral%20on%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20viral%20marketing%2C%20likable%20branding%2C%20word%20of%20mouth%20from%20family%2C%20and%20unbeatable%20prices%20resonated%20with%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Loke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20her%20go-to%20drink%20is%20Mixue's%20Kiwi%20Oolong%20Tea%2C%20which%20costs%20%242.60.%20Loke%20said%20the%20low%20price%20was%20the%20biggest%20factor%20in%20making%20her%20pick%20the%20brand%20over%20other%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEli%20Tun%2C%20a%20student%20waiting%20for%20his%20regular%20order%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%242.20%20Taro%20Milk%20Tea%20%E2%80%94%20said%20he%20first%20spotted%20the%20brand%20in%20Malaysia%20last%20year%20and%20realized%20how%20cheap%20the%20drinks%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20he's%20switched%20from%20buying%20from%20other%20popular%20bubble%20tea%20brands%20in%20Singapore%2C%20like%20LiHo%20Tea%20or%20KOI%20The%CC%81%2C%20saying%20he%20would%20rather%20pay%20%243%20at%20Mixue%20than%20%246%20for%20a%20similar%20drink%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20looking%20for%20the%20cream%20of%20the%20crop%20of%20drinks%2C%20just%20something%20to%20drink%20while%20going%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Tun%2C%2019%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENathanael%20Chow%2C%20an%20investment%20consultant%2C%20said%20he%20always%20gets%20the%20Signature%20King%20Cone%20at%20Mixue%20%E2%80%94%20vanilla%20soft-serve%20ice%20cream%20in%20a%20tall%20waffle%20cone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChow%20said%20he%20was%20drawn%20to%20the%20brand%20because%20of%20the%20brand's%20catchy%20jingle%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20%26quot%3BOh!%20Susanna.%26quot%3B%20Some%20Mixue%20outlets%20play%20the%20jingle%20at%20the%20store%2C%20though%20the%20shop%20BI%20visited%20did%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220827015a-755e-4055-a093-4da5ff0470cb%5C%22%3EMixue's%20success%20lies%20in%20courting%20China's%20cost-conscious%20buyers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJason%20Yu%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20for%20Greater%20China%20at%20the%20UK-based%20consumer%20research%20group%20Kantar%20Worldpanel%2C%20said%20Mixue's%20edge%20in%20China's%20highly%20competitive%20bubble%20tea%20market%20is%20that%20most%20of%20its%20products%20are%20priced%20under%20RMB%2010%2C%20or%20about%20%241.40.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20very%20attractive%20to%20consumers%20in%20the%20lower%20tier%20cities%20and%20towns%2C%26quot%3B%20Yu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlexandra%20Leung%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Monogic%2C%20a%20food%20and%20beverage%20marketing%20and%20public%20relations%20agency%20in%20Singapore%20and%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20said%20Mixue's%20success%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20having%20small%20shops%20in%20high-traffic%20areas%2C%20particularly%20around%20campuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20approach%20not%20only%20captures%20a%20significant%20customer%20base%20but%20also%20ensures%20high%20foot%20traffic%20and%20brand%20loyalty%2C%20especially%20among%20students%20who%20frequently%20consume%20their%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20Leung%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20other%20bubble%20tea%20brands%20have%20been%20focusing%20on%20premium%20positioning%20with%20prices%20above%20RMB%2020%20in%20tier%201%20cities%20like%20Beijing%20and%20Shanghai%2C%20Mixue%20%26quot%3Bsuccessfully%20established%20its%20presence%20in%20lower-tier%20cities%20where%20competition%20is%20less%20intense%2C%26quot%3B%20Leung%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20seen%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fbubble-tea-billionaires-china-ipos-baicha-baidao-mixue-stock-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebubble%20tea%20IPO%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20February%2C%20Guming%20Holdings%20had%20its%20Hong%20Kong%20IPO.%20Sichuan%20Baicha%20Baidao%20Industrial%20Co%20%E2%80%94%20also%20known%20as%20Chabaidao%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20went%20public%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20last%20April%2C%20although%20its%20stock%20is%20trading%20well%20below%20its%20IPO%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Mixue%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-biggest-fast-food-chain-mixue-china-bubble-tea-ipo-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740994605000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c541f2b8b41a9673f972c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-biggest-fast-food-chain-mixue-china-bubble-tea-ipo-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chain%2C%20which%20has%20over%2045%2C000%20stores%20worldwide%2C%20has%20attracted%20customers%20with%20cheap%20ice%20cream%20and%20bubble%20tea.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abharade%40insider.com%20(Aditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-biggest-fast-food-chain-mixue-china-bubble-tea-ipo-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Six%20Actors%2