20that%20X%20CEO%20Linda%20Yaccarino%20and%20a%20lieutenant%20had%20pushed%20IPG%20to%20spend%20more%20money%20on%20X.%20IPG%20execs%20interpreted%20the%20message%20as%20a%20reminder%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration%20could%20impede%20a%20proposed%20merger%20with%20ad%20giant%20Omnicom%2C%20the%20Journal%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20ad%20industry%20insiders%20said%20that%20if%20X%20really%20used%20these%20tactics%2C%20they%20felt%20it%20would%20amount%20to%20bullying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20make%20spending%20commitments%20on%20behalf%20of%20clients%20to%20any%20partner%20or%20platform%2C%20and%20decision-making%20authority%20always%20rests%20with%20the%20client%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20IPG%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EX%20and%20Yaccarino%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Linda%20Yaccarino%20on%20the%20stage%20at%20Vox%20Media's%202023%20Code%20Conference%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65153aabeee46600193bbd28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELinda%20Yaccarino%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20X%2C%20appeared%20in%20a%20recent%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20report.%3Cp%3EJerod%20Harris%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ee946c81-fc9e-4c69-9439-315536d11360%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EX%20has%20been%20attracting%20advertisers%2C%20but%20long-term%20success%20is%20far%20from%20certain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20X%20has%20attracted%20advertisers%2C%20new%20and%20old%2C%20in%20recent%20months%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20big%20names%20like%20Apple%20%E2%80%94%20its%20business%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20booming.%20Marketing%20research%20company%20WARC%20estimates%20that%20X%20will%20pull%20in%20%241.96%20billion%20in%20global%20ad%20revenue%20in%202025%2C%20down%2011%25%20from%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94