%20in%20previous%20years%2C%20Michael%20Beach%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20adtech%20company%20Cross%20Screen%20Media%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPre-Elon%20Musk%2C%20their%20adtech%20was%20so%20bad%20we%20moved%20spend%20away%20from%20Twitter%2C%26quot%3B%20Beach%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20technology%20has%20improved%2C%20and%20small%20advertisers%20understand%20that%20the%20inventory%20is%20undervalued%20versus%20other%20platforms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20top%20media%20buyer%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20advertising%20money%20was%20increasingly%20being%20used%20to%20hedge%20against%20political%20risk%20%E2%80%94%20and%20often%2C%20these%20decisions%20were%20being%20made%20by%20the%20CEOs%20of%20big%20corporations%20versus%20the%20chief%20marketing%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELou%20Paskalis%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20marketing%20consultancy%20AJL%20Advisory%2C%20said%20this%20kind%20of%20fraught%20political%20situation%20makes%20the%20job%20of%20a%20CMO%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%2010%25%20of%20my%20ad%20budget%20has%20to%20be%20allocated%26quot%3B%20to%20risk%20mitigation%2C%20Paskalis%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bmy%20CFO%20isn't%20going%20to%20reduce%20my%20business%20goals%20by%2010%25%20%E2%80%94%20he's%20simply%20going%20to%20say%2C%20you%20need%20to%20deliver%20your%20goals%20with%20the%2090%25%20of%20your%20budget%20that%20is%20investable%20'rationally.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e6b81987-5b39-4726-a705-c26fbd447490%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMusk%20versus%20advertisers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20takeover%20of%20the%20platform%20in%202022%20laid%20the%20groundwork%20for%20the%20current%20relationship%20between%20X%20and%20the%20ad%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20wave%20of%20advertisers%20pulled%20away%20from%20X%20over%20concerns%20about%20brand%20safety%2C%20ad%20performance%2C%20and%20the%20return%20of%20banned%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20X%20didn't%20go%20down%20without%20a%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-x-lawsuit-advertisers-boycott-antitrust-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20several%20of%20its%20advertisers%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20Mars%20and%20CVS%20Health%20%E2%80%94%20accusing%20them%20of%20illegally%20conspiring%20to%20boycott%20the%20platform%20through%20their%20membership%20in%20a%20now-defunct%20industry%20initiative%20called%20the%20Global%20Alliance%20for%20Responsible%20Media.%20X%20has%20since%20added%20several%20more%20brands%20to%20that%20complaint%20as%20defendants%2C%20including%20Colgate%2C%20Lego%2C%20and%20Shell.%20Unilever%20was%20initially%20named%20as%20a%20defendant%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fxnews%2Fstatus%2F1844737849456771425%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereached%20an%20agreement%20with%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20terms%20of%20which%20weren't%20disclosed%20by%20either%20party%20%E2%80%94%20and%20was%20dropped%20from%20the%20suit%20in%20October.%20Unilever%20said%20X%20had%20committed%20to%20meeting%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Flegal%2Felon-musks-x-drops-unilever-advertiser-boycott-lawsuit-2024-10-11%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresponsibility%20standards%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20brand%20safety%20and%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fad-group-to-suspend-garm-initiative-following-elon-musk-lawsuit-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGARM%20shut%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20days%20after%20the%20X%20lawsuit%20was%20filed%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20a%20small%20nonprofit%20with%20limited%20resources.%20Its%20parent%20organization%2C%20the%20World%20Federation%20of%20Advertisers%2C%20has%20maintained%20that%20it%20plans%20to%20fight%20the%20suit%20and%20didn't%20contravene%20antitrust%20laws.%20The%20litigation%20is%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJim%20Jordan%2C%20the%20cha