s%20revoked%2C%20experts%20said%20they%20may%20be%20required%20to%20leave%20Canada%20unless%20they%20successfully%20appeal.%20However%2C%20the%20legal%20costs%20for%20appeals%20start%20at%20C%241%2C500%2C%20with%20no%20guarantee%20of%20success.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20telling%20our%20Canadian%20clients%20to%20document%20everything%20-%20every%20hour%20worked%20and%20every%20address%20change%20should%20be%20reported%20within%20seven%20days.%20Canada%20has%20shifted%20from%20welcoming%20to%20suspicious%2C%20and%20students%20must%20adapt%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada's%20tightening%20stance%20on%20immigration%20is%20also%20affecting%20the%20number%20of%20study%20permits%20granted%20to%20Indian%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%2040%20per%20cent%20drop%20in%20study%20permits%20issued%20to%20Indian%20students%20since%20Q4%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20Siddharth%20Iyer%2C%20chief%20operating%20officer%20of%20OneStep%20Global%20told%20ET.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20Fall%202025%20applicants%20face%20the%20new%20C%2420%2C635%20GIC%20(guaranteed%20investment%20certificate)%20requirement%20-%20a%20massive%20financial%20hurdle%20for%20middle-class%20Indian%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Indian%20students%20make%20up%20nearly%2035-40%20per%20cent%20of%20Canada's%20international%20student%20population.%20The%20new%20regulations%20are%20likely%20to%20impact%20them%2C%20along%20with%20Indian%20employees%2C%20and%20temporary%20resident%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EChange%20In%20Canada's%20Visa%20Programme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20Canadian%20government's%20push%20to%20reduce%20illegal%20migration%2C%20the%20country%20has%20introduced%20big%20changes%20to%20its%20immigration%20regulations%2C%20authorising%20border%20officials%20to%20cancel%20temporary%20resident%20documents%20such%20as%20electronic%20travel%20authorisations%20(eTAs)%20and%20temporary%20resident%20visas%20(TRVs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20amended%20rules%2C%20Canadian%20immigration%20and%20border%20officers%20can%20cancel%20any%20individual's%20eTAs%2C%20TRVs%2C%20work%20permits%2C%20and%20study%20permits%20if%20their%20status%20or%20circumstances%20change%2C%20making%20them%20ineligible%20or%20inadmissible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20can%20even%20cancel%20any%20person's%20permits%20if%20they%20are%20not%20convinced%20that%20the%20individual%20will%20leave%20Canada%20upon%20the%20expiration%20of%20their%20authorised%20stay%20and%20if%20their%20documents%20are%20lost%2C%20stolen%2C%20destroyed%2C%20or%20issued%20based%20on%20an%20administrative%20error.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20students%20can%20also%20have%20their%20immigration%20papers%20cancelled%20if%20they%20are%20denied%20a%20work%20or%20study%20visa.%20However%2C%20the%20rules%20ensure%20that%20the%20immigration%20and%20border%20authorities%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20who%20can%20cancel%20these%20visas%2C%20to%20avoid%20any%20unauthorised%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20if%20any%20student's%20study%20permit%20is%20revoked%2C%20they%20might%20face%20trouble%20finishing%20their%20studies%20or%20moving%20to%20work%20permits%20after%20graduation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada%20is%20among%20the%20most%20preferred%20destinations%20for%20Indian%20students%2C%20workers%2C%20and%20legal%20migrants.%20Students%20alone%2C%20currently%20pursuing%20their%20higher%20education%20in%20Canada%2C%20account%20for%20more%20than%204.2%20lakh%20Indian%20nationals%20as%20per%20government%20data.%C2%A0The%20amended%20rules%20follow%20a%20series%20of%20changes%20to%20Ottawa's%20immigration%20framework%2C%20including%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20Student%20Direct%20Stream%20(SDS)%20visa%20programme%20in%20late%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740993060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F07dmtsl_canada-immigration-reuter