0target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrossing%20the%20threshold%20of%2040%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20slightly%20delusional%20hopefulness%20of%20youth%20has%20faded.%20New%20aches%20and%20pains%20are%20creeping%20in.%20People%20may%20be%20disappointed%20in%20how%20their%20life%20has%20turned%20out%20and%20not%20super%20jazzed%20about%20the%20future.%20Those%20in%20the%20sandwich%20phase%20of%20caregiving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedicine.umich.edu%2Fdept%2Fpsychiatry%2Fnews%2Farchive%2F202212%2F%25E2%2580%259Csandwich-generation%25E2%2580%259D-study-shows-challenges-caring-both-kids-aging-parents%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20more%20financial%20and%20emotional%20troubles%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20their%20peers.%20Middle%20age%20means%20you're%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2Fglobal_20160825_happiness_stress_age.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EU-shaped%20curve%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20satisfaction.%20We're%20happy%20when%20we're%20young%2C%20then%20we%20have%20a%20bad%20time%20in%20our%2040s%20or%20so%2C%20and%20then%20we%20get%20happy%20again%20when%20we're%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20younger%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20as%20many%20responsibilities%2C%20or%20they're%20not%20as%20taxing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lindsey%20Anderson%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%20who%20studies%20aging.%20%26quot%3BThen%2C%20you're%20in%20this%20middle%20age%20trying%20to%20figure%20life%20out%2C%20where%20you%20have%20children%2C%20maybe%20aging%20parents%2C%20a%20career.%20You%20have%20these%20life-course%20milestones%20that%20are%20bigger%20and%20heavier%20that%20you%20have%20to%20lift.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20the%20challenges%20and%20stresses%20that%20come%20with%20adulthood%2C%20millennials%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-gen-z-socks-jeans-brands-aging-cash-advertising-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealso%20losing%20the%20automatic%20cool%20factor%20bestowed%20by%20youth%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Their%20socks%20are%20too%20short%20and%20their%20hair%20is%20parted%20wrong%20and%20they%20have%20absolutely%20no%20idea%20what%20is%20happening%20with%20pants%20anymore.%20Brands%20are%20speaking%20to%20them%20differently%2C%20with%20buzzwords%20like%20%26quot%3Bsensible%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bpractical%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsafe.%26quot%3B%20The%20good%20news%20is%20maybe%20they're%20so%20wrapped%20up%20in%20the%20trappings%20of%20being%20a%20grown-up%20they%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20care%20about%20whatever%20latest%20trend%20they%20are%20behind%20on.%20%26quot%3BJeans%20that%20are%20clean%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20only%20goal%20when%20you%20have%20a%20screaming%20toddler%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20being%20part%20of%20this%20generation%20that%20is%20now%20parenting%20and%20managing%20and%20the%20adults%20in%20every%20sense%20of%20the%20term%20and%20managers%20in%20every%20sense%20of%20the%20term%2C%20maybe%20I'm%20too%20exhausted%20to%20go%20to%20happy%20hour%20the%20way%20that%20I%20used%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Lovell%2C%20a%20career%20coach%20from%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fifunny.co%2Fpicture%2F13-year-old-me-don-t-tell-me-what-to-2ILbSYSFB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20meme%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20flies%20around%20online.%20It%20goes%3A%20%26quot%3B13-year-old%20me%3A%20Don't%20tell%20me%20what%20to%20do.%20Me%20now%3A%20Could%20someone%20tell%20me%20exactly%2C%20in%20chronological%20order%20and%20with%20great%20detail%2C%20what%20I%20have%20to%20do%3F%26quot%3B%20It%20crystallizes%20the%20current%20millennial%20life%20stage.%20Like%20it%20or%20not%2C%20the%20avocado-toast-loving%2C%20brunch-obsessed%20generation%20is%20now%20running%20the%20show.%20And%20many%20millennials%20do%20not%20like%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2C%20of%20course%2C%20upsides%20here.%20Once%20you%20step%20into%20the%20role%20of%20being%20the%20grown-up%2C%20you%20come%20to%20understand%20that%20you%20can%20trust%20yourself%20to%20take%20on%20the%20responsibilities%20that%20perhaps%20once%20felt%20daunting.%20There's%20something%20freeing%20in%20being%20the%20decider%20and%20developing%20that%20level%20of%20autonomy.%20It's%20also%20nice%20to%20have%20yourself%20together%20a%20little%20more.%20The%20tasks%20you're%20taking%20on%20are%20ones%20you're%20prepared%20for%2C%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20realize%20it.%20It's%20sort%20of%20like%20you're%20lifting%20weights%20in%20the%20gym%20for%20years%2C%20and%20over%20time%2C%20you%20get%20to%20the%20point%20where%20you%20can%20pick%20really%20heavy%20things%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMillennials%20are%20trying%20to%20do%20things%20differently%20and%20better%20than%20generations%20past%2C%20to%20varying%20degrees%20of%20success.%20As%20much%20as%20they%20may%20want%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bcool%26quot%3B%20dad%2C%20sometimes%2C%20they%20just%20have%20to%20be%20a%20dad.%20We%20compare%20ourselves%20with%20the%20models%20we%20had%20as%20children%20and%20young%20adults%2C%20meaning%20our%20parents%2C%20our%20grandparents%2C%20our%20early%20managers%2C%20and%20our%20older%20coworkers.%20We%20take%20cues%20on%20what%20to%20do%20and%20how%20to%20act%20from%20them%2C%20or%20at%20least%20from%20how%20we%20thought%20they%20were%20doing%20things.%20And%2C%20oftentimes%2C%20we%20realize%20they%20had%20a%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20a%20new%20appreciation%20for%20the%20work%20that%20your%20parents%20or%20your%20manager%20or%20whoever%20the%20model%20was%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20of%20realizing%20you're%20the%20grown-up%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20excitement%20and%20fear%20that%20come%20with%20it%20%E2%80%94%20isn't%20unique%20to%20millennials.%20Baby%20boomers%20did%20it%2C%20Gen%20X%20did%20it%2C%20and%20Gen%20Z%2C%20you'll%20get%20there%2C%20too.%20Millennials%20are%20doing%20it%20in%20the%20age%20of%20social%20media%2C%20meaning%20they%20get%20to%20watch%20their%20peers%2C%20commiserate%2C%20and%20wonder%20whether%20they're%20falling%20short.%20The%20internet%20is%20a%20space%20for%20endless%20suggestions%20on%20how%20to%20do%20things%20%26quot%3Bright.%26quot%3B%20Part%20of%20being%20the%20adult%20in%20the%20room%20is%20sifting%20through%20all%20that%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20answer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20eventually%20just%20going%20with%20%26quot%3Bgood%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-adults-work-parents-bosses-children-homeownership-responsibility-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740992822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0c4ef69253ccddf97d1c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-adults-work-parents-bosses-children-homeownership-responsibility-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20becoming%20bosses%20at%20work%20to%20taking%20care%20of%20their%20own%20parents%2C%20the%20avocado%20toast%20generation%20is%20now%20in%20charge%20and%20everyone%20is%20scrambling.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22estewart%40insider.com%20(Emily%20Stewart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-adults-work-parents-bosses-children-homeownership-responsibility-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Rohit%20Sharma%20Shouldn't%20Be%20On%20Team'%3A%20Trinamool%20MP%20Echoes%20Shama%20Mohamed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20spokesperson%20Shama%20Mohamed's%20remarks%20on%20Team%20India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20may%20have%20drawn%20a%20sharp%20rebuke%20from%20the%20party%20command%20but%20has%20found%20some%20support%20from%20an%20unlikely%20quarter.%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Sougata%20Ray%20said%20Ms%20Mohamed%20had%20not%20said%20anything%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20news%20agency%20IANS%2C%20Mr%20Ray%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20heard%20that%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20performance%20has%20been%20quite%20poor.%20He%20scored%20one%20century%2C%20but%20other%20than%20that%2C%20he%20gets%20out%20after%20scoring%202%2C%203%2C%204%2C%20or%205%20runs.%20He%20shouldn't%20be%20(on%20the%20team).%20India%20wins%20because%20the%20other%20players%20play%20well%2C%20but%20the%20captain%20doesn't%20contribute.%26quot%3B%20The%20veteran%20leader%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Shama%20Mohamed%20has%20said%20is%20correct.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EKolkata%2C%20West%20Bengal%3A%20On%20Congress%20leader%20Shama%20Mohamed%20fat%20shaming%20Team%20India%20captian%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20TMC%20MP%20Saugata%20Roy%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20heard%20that%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20performance%20has%20been%20quite%20poor.%20He%20scored%20one%20century%2C%20but%20other%20than%20that%2C%20he%20gets%20out%20after%20scoring%202%2C%203%2C%204%2C%20or%205%20runs.%20He%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fh89cNP43jO%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fh89cNP43jO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20IANS%20(%40ians_india)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fians_india%2Fstatus%2F1896458937735795091%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%203%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader's%20harsh%20criticism%20of%20Mr%20Sharma%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20Hitman%20for%20his%20aggressive%20batting%2C%20has%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20during%20India%20vs%20New%20Zealand%20Champions%20Trophy%20clash%20yesterday%2C%20Ms%20Mohamed%20said%20Rohit%20Sharma%20%26quot%3Bis%20fat%20for%20a%20sportsman%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BNeed%20to%20lose%20weight!%20And%20ofcourse%20the%20most%20unimpressive%20Captain%20India%20has%20ever%20had%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20remarks%20triggered%20a%20row%20and%20the%20BJP%20latched%20on%20to%20them%20to%20question%20the%20Congress's%20patriotism%2C%20Ms%20Mohamed%20deleted%20the%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20distanced%20itself%20from%20the%20remarks%20and%20said%20they%20do%20not%20reflect%20the%20party's%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawan%20Khera%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20party's%20publicity%20department%2C%20said%20she%20had%20been%20asked%20to%20delete%20the%20social%20media%20posts.%20%26quot%3BDr.%20Shama%20Mohammed%2C%20National%20Spokesperson%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%2C%20made%20certain%20remarks%20about%20a%20cricketing%20legend%20that%20do%20not%20reflect%20the%20party's%20position.%20She%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20delete%20the%20concerned%20social%20media%20posts%20from%20X%20and%20has%20been%20advised%20to%20exercise%20greater%20caution%20in%20the%20future.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20holds%20the%20contributions%20of%20sporting%20icons%20in%20the%20highest%20regard%20and%20does%20not%20endorse%20any%20statements%20that%20undermine%20their%20legacy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khera%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20BJP%20reacted%20sharply%20and%20asked%20if%20the%20Congress%20now%20expects%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20play%20cricket.%20%26quot%3BShame%20on%20Congress!%20Now%20they%20are%20going%20after%20the%20Indian%20Cricket%20Captain!%20Do%20they%20expect%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20now%20play%20cricket%20after%20failing%20in%20Indian%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Pradeep%20Bhandari%20said%20in%20reply%20to%20the%20Congress%20leader's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Bhandari%20said%20the%20Congress%20spokesperson's%20remark%20reflects%20the%20party's%20Emergency%20mindset.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20insult%20to%20every%20patriot%20who%20supports%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20through%20thick%20and%20thin.%20I%20question%20the%20Congress's%20criticism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirty-seven-year-old%20Rohit%20Sharma%20took%20over%20as%20Team%20India%20captain%20in%202023.%20Under%20his%20leadership%2C%20India%20won%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20last%20year%20and%20two%20Asia%20Cup%20trophies%20earlier.%20He%20has%20a%20stellar%20record%20in%20IPL%20too.%20As%20Mumbai%20Indians%20captain%2C%20he%20has%20led%20the%20team%20to%20five%20IPL%20titles.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740992760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fl8f0isd8_rohit-sharma_625x300_03_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frohit-sharma-shama-mohamed-sougata-ray-rohit-sharma-shouldnt-be-on-team-trinamool-mp-echoes-shama-mohamed-7836392%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20spokesperson%20Shama%20Mohamed's%20remarks%20on%20Team%20India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20may%20have%20drawn%20a%20sharp%20rebuke%20from%20the%20party%20command%20but%20has%20found%20some%20support%20from%20an%20unlikely%20quarter%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frohit-sharma-shama-mohamed-sougata-ray-rohit-sharma-shouldnt-be-on-team-trinamool-mp-echoes-shama-mohamed-7836392%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%20records%20forward%20dollar%20position%20undermines%20forex%20reserves%20comfort%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740992693000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22