%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sketch%20began%20with%20Johnson's%20Trump%20introducing%20himself%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BPresident%20and%20CEO%20of%20Gaza%20Hotel%20and%20Casino%26quot%3B%20and%20telling%20Zelensky%2C%20%26quot%3BWelcome%20to%20this%20incredible%20trap%3B%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20big%2C%20beautiful%20trap%2C%20and%20we're%20going%20to%20attack%20him%20very%20soon%20for%20no%20reason.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBowen%20Yang's%20JD%20Vance%20jumped%20in%20with%3A%20%26quot%3BWatch%20out%2C%20'cause%20this%20kitty's%20got%20claws.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comedic%20highlight%20of%20the%20skit%20came%20when%20Johnson's%20Trump%20mockingly%20thanked%20Zelensky%20for%20dressing%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bcasual%20Star%20Trek%26quot%3B%20outfit%2C%20saying%20he%20loved%20the%20show%20because%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20no%20DEI.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20white%20guy%20was%20the%20leader%2C%20and%20he%20bossed%20around%20Spock%2C%20who%20I%20believe%20was%20Guatemalan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20skit%20also%20showed%20Trump%20urging%20Zelensky%20to%20apologise%20to%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20and%20suggested%20that%20he%20offer%20his%20wife%20to%20Putin%20as%20a%20peace%20offering.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20dramatic%20outburst%20from%20Yang's%20JD%20Vance%2C%20who%2C%20in%20an%20exaggerated%20comedic%20rant%2C%20shouted%20at%20Zelensky%20for%20not%20expressing%20enough%20gratitude%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20happened%20to%20'thank%20you'%3F%20You%20haven't%20said%20thank%20you%20once%20in%20the%20past%2015%20seconds%20I've%20been%20yelling%20at%20you!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20segment%20further%20satirised%20Trump%2C%20with%20him%20listing%20off%20random%20items%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20the%20cards.%20I%20have%20Skip.%20I%20have%20Draw%20Four.%20I%20have%20Reverse.%20I%20have%20Get%20Out%20of%20Jail%20Free%20-%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20gave%20me%20that%20one.%20I%20have%20Pikachu%20and%20Charmander%20and%20Charizard.%20All%20I'm%20missing%20is%20a%20Charmeleon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%20moment%20that%20drew%20Musk's%20attention.%20Mike%20Myers%2C%20playing%20Musk%2C%20entered%20the%20scene%20dressed%20in%20a%20long%20black%20coat%2C%20holding%20a%20chainsaw%2C%20and%20declared%2C%20%26quot%3BThey're%20saying%20I'm%20firing%20people%20with%20no%20cause.%20But%20I%20do%20have%20cause.%20It's%20'cause%20I%20feel%20like%20it.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Real%20Oval%20Office%20Clash%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20skit%20was%20a%20satirical%20take%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fzelensky-leaves-white-house-after-heated-trump-clash-at-white-house-7819167%5C%22%3Eheated%20White%20House%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20last%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20sought%20security%20guarantees%20from%20the%20US%20amid%20Ukraine's%20ongoing%20war%20with%20Russia%2C%20while%20Trump%20pressured%20him%20to%20make%20concessions%20for%20a%20swift%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETensions%20peaked%20when%20Vance%20accused%20Zelensky%20of%20failing%20to%20express%20enough%20gratitude%20for%20US%20aid%2C%20despite%20the%20Ukrainian%20President%20beginning%20the%20meeting%20with%20words%20of%20thanks.%20The%20conversation%20grew%20more%20confrontational%20as%20Trump%20interrupted%2C%20telling%20Zelensky%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20tell%20us%20what%20we're%20going%20to%20feel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20ended%20without%20a%20resolution.%20Trump%20cancelled%20a%20planned%20joint%20news%20conference%20and%20the%20signing%20of%20a%20minerals%20agreement.%20The%20Ukrainian%20delegation%20was%20asked%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740989760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F0rccpqh8_elon-musk-snl-video_625x300_03_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2