video-us-firefighters-tackle-devastating-wildfires-in-carolinas-amid-dry-air-gusty-winds-7835685%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHave%20Babies%20Now%26quot%3B%3A%20MK%20Stalin's%20Message%20For%20Newlyweds%20Is%20A%20Delimitation%20Jab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sarcastic%20jab%20at%20the%20Centre's%20delimitation%20plans%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20has%20urged%20newlywed%20couples%20to%20plan%20families%20immediately%20so%20that%20the%20state%20gets%20an%20advantage%20when%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20is%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20wedding%20function%20of%20a%20DMK%20district%20secretary%20at%20Nagapattinam%2C%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20he%20would%20earlier%20ask%20newlyweds%20to%20take%20their%20time%20before%20they%20plan%20a%20family.%20%26quot%3BBut%20now%20with%20policies%20such%20as%20delimitation%20that%20the%20Union%20Government%20is%20planning%20to%20implement%2C%20we%20cannot%20say%20that.%20We%20focused%20on%20family%20planning%20and%20succeeded%20and%20were%20pushed%20into%20a%20situation%20such%20as%20this.%20So%20I%20would%20now%20urge%20newlyweds%20to%20immediately%20have%20babies%20and%20give%20them%20good%20Tamil%20names%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20DMK%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20been%20leading%20the%20delimitation%20charge%20against%20the%20government.%20Delimitation%20is%20the%20process%20of%20redrawing%20boundaries%20of%20parliamentary%20and%20Assembly%20constituencies%20to%20reflect%20changes%20in%20population%20over%20time.%20DMK%20leader%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20has%20contended%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%2C%20expected%20to%20be%20conducted%20after%202026%2C%20will%20put%20southern%20states%20at%20a%20disadvantage.%20These%20states%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20implemented%20family%20planning%20effectively%20over%20the%20years%20and%20this%20population%20control%20may%20work