ion%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThey%20set%20up%20colour-coded%20bamboo%20bins%20for%20recycling%20and%20composting%20throughout%20the%20venue%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20team%20actively%20guided%20guests%20with%20signage%20and%20informative%20posters%2C%20making%20waste%20sorting%20both%20simple%20and%20engaging.%20Every%20item%20of%20waste%20was%20meticulously%20categorised%20and%20sent%20to%20the%20appropriate%20recycling%20centres%20and%20composting%20facilities%2C%20ensuring%20that%20absolutely%20nothing%20from%20the%20wedding%20ended%20up%20in%20a%20landfill.%20By%20embracing%20zero-waste%20principles%20such%20as%20mindful%20material%20sourcing%2C%20reusable%20decor%2C%20and%20responsible%20waste%20management%2C%20couples%20can%20drastically%20reduce%20their%20environmental%20footprint.%20More%20importantly%2C%20integrating%20conversations%20around%20sustainability%20into%20the%20celebration%20can%20encourage%20guests%20to%20adopt%20low-waste%20habits%20in%20their%20everyday%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20waste-conscious%20mindset%20even%20extended%20to%20the%20wedding%20favours.%20Instead%20of%20the%20usual%20trinkets%2C%20the%20couple%20chose%20to%20give%20guests%20organic%20honey%20from%20a%20local%20Goan%20apiary%2C%20packaged%20in%20glass%20jars%2C%20sourced%20by%20them.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20honour%20our%20guests%20with%20something%20sustainable%2C%20and%20organic%20honey%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20gift%2C%E2%80%9D%20Svetlana%20shares.%20For%20their%20bridesmaids%20and%20best%20men%2C%20they%20curated%20zero-waste%20gift%20boxes%20containing%20organic%20products%20like%20deodorants%2C%20lip%20balms%2C%20soaps%2C%20and%20moisturisers%2C%20handcrafted%20by%20local%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20transportation%2C%20the%20couple%20took%20steps%20to%20reduce%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20by%20arranging%20shuttle%20buses%20for%20guests.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20minimise%20the%20number%20of%20cars%20at%20the%20wedding%20to%20reduce%20pollution%2C%20so%20we%20organised%20three%20shuttle%20buses%2C%E2%80%9D%20Svetlana%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20asked%20guests%20not%20to%20bring%20physical%20gifts%20but%20instead%20contribute%20to%20a%20social%20impact%20registry%2C%20where%20they%20could%20donate%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345161%2Ftvaran-by-cisco-villgro-empower-women-led-startups-female-entrepreneurs-climate-action%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecauses%20such%20as%20climate%20action%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20disaster%20relief%2C%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%2C%20via%20our%20wedding%20website.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EImpact%20on%20the%20society%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20efforts%20were%20well-received%2C%20with%20about%20200%20guests%20attending%20the%20event.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20they%20generated%20300%20kg%20of%20waste%2C%20including%20approximately%2066%20kg%20of%20recyclable%20waste%20and%20the%20remainder%20biodegradable%2C%20such%20as%20food%20scraps%20and%20coconut%20shells.%20%E2%80%9CEverything%20was%20diverted%20from%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20their%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%2C%20the%20couple%20also%20partnered%20with%20the%20local%20clean-up%20initiative%20%3Cem%3ESaaf%20Samudra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20collecting%20and%20recycling%20250%20kgs%20of%20ocean-bound%20plastic%20from%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20coastline%20on%20behalf%20of%20each%20attendee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20saved%20significantly%20by%20eliminating%20unnecessary%20expenses%2C%20like%20elaborate%20decor%20and%20physical%20invites%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202490px)%20100vw%2C%202490px%5C%22%