y-history-tradition-culture-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeciphering%20the%20instrument%E2%80%99s%20design%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20poetic%20metaphors.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20won%E2%80%99t%20have%20direct%20information%20about%20the%20instrument%20but%20rather%20it%20would%20be%20hidden%20behind%20%3Cem%3Euvamai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(metaphors%20in%20Tamil)%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Tharun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPhrases%20like%20%E2%80%98The%20sound%20of%20Yazh%20was%20like%20honey%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20bend%20of%20Yazh%20was%20like%20the%20belly%20of%20an%20eight-month%20pregnant%20woman%E2%80%99%20are%20just%20entry-level%20metaphors%3B%20there%20are%20many%20in-depth%20ones.%20Based%20on%20these%20references%2C%20we%20started%20to%20trace%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20instrument.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20620px)%20100vw%2C%20620px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-96_11zon-1740452568.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Creating%20a%20yazh%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-96_11zon-1740452568.jpg%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-96_11zon-1740452568-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-96_11zon-1740452568-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-96_11zon-1740452568-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-409090%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22413%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAncient%20Tamil%20literature%20helped%20Tharun%20to%20decode%20the%20design%20and%20sound%20of%20Yazh.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Tharun%20a%20year%20of%20research%20and%20designing%20to%20create%20the%20first%20playable%20Yazh.%20He%20worked%20on%20the%20woodwork%20himself%2C%20while%20a%20craftsman%20from%20Madurai%20assisted%20with%20the%20brass%20components%2C%20and%20another%20artisan%20helped%20with%20the%20stand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20were%20involved%20in%20research%2C%20I%20started%20making%20the%20instrument%20parallelly.%20Once%20I%20cracked%20the%20design%2C%20I%20started%20with%20the%20woodwork%20myself.%20For%20the%20brass%20work%2C%20we%20had%20a%20craftsman%20from%20Madurai%2C%20and%20we%20had%20another%20person%20make%20the%20stand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20only%20person%20involved%20in%20the%20design%2C%20Tharun%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20woodwork%2C%20while%20outsourcing%20experts%20from%20Chennai%2C%20Pondicherry%2C%20and%20Madurai%20to%20carve%20wings%2C%20the%20body%20etc.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20the%20best%20people%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20people%20who%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20craft%20are%20just%20a%20handful%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Tharun.%20He%20adds%20that%20around%2030%20people%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20the%20instruments%20are%20handcrafted%20with%20precision%20to%20detail.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20CMC%20machines%20involved.%20The%20carving%20is%20handmade%2C%20and%20the%20machines