%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20as%20if%20nature%20had%20been%20patiently%20waiting%20for%20a%20helping%20hand%20to%20tip%20the%20scales%20back%20towards%20equilibrium!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%20inspiring%20is%20the%20ripple%20effect%20these%20solar%20installations%20create%20%E2%80%94%20local%20stakeholders%20also%20benefit%20from%20this%20endeavour%2C%20as%20many%20of%20the%20water%20lines%20are%20directed%20to%20anti-poaching%20outposts%2C%20freeing%20forest%20guards%20from%20weekly%20treks%20for%20water%20and%20enabling%20them%20to%20focus%20on%20safeguarding%20wildlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20innovation%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20ecological%3B%20it%20aimed%20to%20mitigate%20human-wildlife%20conflicts%2C%20an%20ever-present%20reality%20threatening%20both%20communities%20and%20wild%20species%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Sarita%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%20installing%20solar%20pumps%2C%20water%20could%20be%20provided%20consistently%20across%20various%20zones%20within%20the%20reserves%2C%20ensuring%20animals%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20wander%20into%20human%20habitats%20in%20search%20of%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fsolar-pumps-2-1740399564.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22So%20far%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20completed%20170%20solar%20water%20pump%20installations%20in%2025%20forests%20and%20wildlife%20sanctuaries%20across%20seven%20states.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fso